snippet.title: Vector Velocity - Trailer [VR, HTC Vive, Oculus Rift]
snippet.description:
Trailer for Vector Velocity, a virtual reality parkour-style game that challenges you to race as fast as you can by climbing, jumping, sliding and more. Developed by David Mulder, available for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/vector-velocity
